criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with histological and imaging findings-confirmed hormone
             receptor-positive/human epidermal growth factor receptor 2-negative breast cancer;

          -  postmenopausal patients;

          -  eligible patients receiving one or more treatment strategies who are followed up in
             the center where they receive treatment;

          -  provision of written informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age < 18 years;

          -  pregnant woman;

          -  participating in other clinical trials.
